{"tid":2407492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華惡「壩」攔水 湄公河聯盟炮轟","createTime":"2021-02-14T05:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T09:52:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d9cea76ccf5c940ab27c7f2e0b69c330452632ea","tid":2407492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210214/5OO6M4TL6REYVAJ3ZEJLMTM2KI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210214%2F5OO6M4TL6REYVAJ3ZEJLMTM2KI%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=5232756a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210214%2F5OO6M4TL6REYVAJ3ZEJLMTM2KI%2F&h=eb742a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210214/5OO6M4TL6REYVAJ3ZEJLMTM2KI/</a><br />\n<br />\n華惡「壩」攔水 湄公河聯盟炮轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4yz2nTCdp-icXaka1TzKMkzVgnM=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q2JLH7HWB5EWPA24S53YYWMTZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4yz2nTCdp-icXaka1TzKMkzVgnM%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ2JLH7HWB5EWPA24S53YYWMTZI.jpg&h=57b26111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國被指興建水壩，引發湄公河下游多國乾旱。<br />\n<br />\n中國近年在湄公河上游建大壩發電，讓手握限水大權的中方變相可操縱多個下游國家的生態命脈。由位處湄公河下游的泰國、老撾、越南及柬埔寨所組成的湄公河委員會前日發表聲明指，湄公河水位近日已降至「令人擔憂的水平」，呼籲中方共享水壩排水量等水文數據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或致千萬民眾無飯開<br />\n<br />\n聲明指湄公河水位近期明顯下降，委員會認為現象與低降雨量及中方水壩有關。當中，雲南省景洪大壩向下游的一月初排水量約為每秒785立方米，一月中旬更升至每秒1,400立方米。不過，二月排水量再次下降，截至上周四，排水量僅為每秒800立方米。委員會呼籲中方對大壩水庫進行放水，讓下游水位恢復正常。委員會又警告，水位下降不但影響魚類遷徙、農業、交通運輸等，亦對湄公河沿岸數千萬民眾的糧食來源造成危機。委員會秘書處技術支持部主任呼籲中方，與下游國家共享相關水壩排水計劃及水文數據等，協助湄公河下游國家作出更有效的風險管理。<br />\n<br />\n湄公河（中國境內稱瀾滄江）發源於中國青藏高原，全長4,350多公里，流經老撾、緬甸、泰國、柬埔寨和越南五個東盟國，最後流入南海，估計東南亞有6,000萬人依賴湄公河的資源。隨着中國在湄公河上游興建11座水壩進行水力發電，這些國家屢與中國因湄公河水位驟降發生糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"30bf6674f5e0910d62ff4b810d1328578c882314","tid":2407492,"uid":17473,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"憑自己本事攔水，你地嘈乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c024ad8e19b349c15d4e1a85cb1488319b05236","tid":2407492,"uid":81113,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">請湄公河聯盟托支真嘅炮出嚟先講嘢啦</span><br />\n<br />\n因為支那人唔見棺材唔流眼淚"},{"pid":"3554bfe7adac575c8f5c1e99289fe24b36058a5d","tid":2407492,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bb1488ba0c0ee7d06de19b42a6c21bae0e8846","tid":2407492,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4173fe8ba6c2e101581cfbfe6910217cda5e9908","tid":2407492,"uid":117729,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T06:01:23.000Z","msg":"上游排洪先係考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd162508fb9debcc36cec413eecab543f8931c0","tid":2407492,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30bf6674f5e0910d62ff4b810d1328578c882314","tid":2407492,"uid":17473,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"憑自己本事攔水，你地嘈乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"啲粉紅真係咁講<br />\n<br />\n話自己地方起壩想點就點<br />\n關其他國家差事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24409a78db8ba9ebc7031509dc65590d18d1b320","tid":2407492,"uid":181801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"炸尻爛條壩佢"},{"pid":"a202b4e35248e3ddf45629e66986144c5454e86